## Screenshot // Entire Screen // <Alt> 4 ##
bindsym Mod1+4 exec --no-startup-id maim | xclip -selection clipboard -t image/png
## Screenshot // Selected Region // <Alt> <Shift> 4 ##
bindsym Mod1+Shift+4 exec --no-startup-id maim --select "/home/$USER/Pictures/Screenshots/$(date)"
## CopyQ // Toggle // <Alt> v ##
bindsym Mod1+v exec copyq toggle
## Navigate // Move workspace to next window // <ï…º> x ##
bindsym $mod+x move workspace to output next
